Steps to recreate issue - 
1. User is already logged-in in the MY HYPERSKILL Android app. 
2. User turns off the internet on the device. 
3. Open the MY HYPERSKILL app. 
4. Shows error like "It seems like a network eror". 
5. Turn on the internet of device. 
6. re-open the app. 
7. Boom!!! User gets logged-out of the app. 

Expected - 
User should remain logged-in into their profile. 

Actual - 
User gets logged-out of the app. 
